name: New Shoreham (Block Island) Residents POD
notes: This clinic is for people 18 years of age or older who need their SECOND DOSE of MODERNA vaccine (which needs to be at least 4 weeks after your first dose).  Please do not register for it if you are looking for a first dose and are unable to travel off the island in four weeks to get your corresponding second dose, as there will be no second dose Moderna on the island four weeks from this date. ●●● ENGLISH: This clinic is offering the Moderna COVID-19 vaccine which is for people age 18 and older only. ●●● ESPAÑOL: Esta clínica ofrece la vacuna Moderna contra COVID-19 que es para personas con 18 años o más solamente.. ●●● PORTUGUÊS: Esta clínica está a oferecer a vacina COVID-19 da Moderna, que é apenas para pessoas com 18 anos ou mais.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
